-- Nextel operator NII Holdings files for Chapter 11 in New York court
-- By Guillermo Parra-Bernal
-- Mon Sep 15, 2014 02:32PM EDT
-- None



Sept 15 (Reuters) - NII Holdings Inc <NIHD.O> filed for bankruptcy protection in the United States on Monday as the Nextel operator in Latin America struggles with $5.8 billion in debt and fierce competition in its key markets of Brazil and Mexico.

